cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper deals with feature extraction and representation in computer vision, which is a core topic in the computer vision subfield (cs.CV). The proposed method also involves deep learning, which is a popular research area in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also applies the proposed features to tasks related to robotics (cs.RO) and neural networks (cs.NE).
